Located on Flemington Road, Franklin, Unit 85 is a brand new commercial premises set to capture passing foot traffic from the light rail and bus stop which is situated directly out front. 

Among the fast growing Gungahlin Region, this commercial unit sits 2.5km from Gungahlin Town Centre, 3km from Mitchell Shops, and 9km from the CBD.

For additional information or to book an inspection please contact the exclusive CBRE agents.
